@startuml class_model
!theme plain

title UIM SAP Event Mesh (EVM) - Class Model

package "uim.sap.eventmesh" {
  class EVMConfig
  class EVMServer
  class EVMService
  class EVMStore

  class EVMQueue
  class EVMTopic
  class EVMSubscription
  class EVMMessage
  class EVMWebhook
  class EVMDeadLetter
}

EVMServer --> EVMService
EVMService --> EVMConfig
EVMService --> EVMStore
EVMStore o-- EVMQueue
EVMStore o-- EVMTopic
EVMStore o-- EVMSubscription
EVMStore o-- EVMMessage
EVMStore o-- EVMWebhook
EVMStore o-- EVMDeadLetter

EVMSubscription --> EVMTopic : routes from
EVMSubscription --> EVMQueue : routes to
EVMWebhook --> EVMQueue : delivers from

@enduml
